<l>uraipporuṭ kiḷavi nīṭṭamum varaiyār</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>No one prevents the lengthening<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">nīṭṭam.</foreign></note> of the particle used in addressing [a person].<note place="foot">i.e. of<foreign xml:lang="ta"> amma,</foreign> e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">ammā koṟṟā.</foreign></note></l>
<l>The final <foreign xml:lang="ta">ya</foreign> of the optative <foreign xml:lang="ta">vāḻiya</foreign></l>
<l>is optionally dropped.<note place="foot">E.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">vāḻiya koṟṟā &gt; vāḻikoṟṟā.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
